### 3. Use Java-style Unicode escapes

This is a feature that existed but was undocumented prior to version 3.2 ([JEXL-331][JEXL-331]).  You can use a Java-style Unicode escape inside a string literal.  The hexadecimal value of `\n` is 0x0a, so use:

